        <mxCell id="mKSp-kjD-UKk3Y8Q-u14-1" value="&lt;div&gt;Pregame&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;- - - - - - - - - - - - - -&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;Place the cat and prepare for the game.&lt;br&gt; &lt;/div&gt;" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" vertex="1" parent="1">
